data.description: Fantastic 3 bedroom, 1.5 bath, split level home in Dana heights. This home has only had 2 owners. Meticulously maintained and is completely move-in ready. Updated bathrooms, downstairs flooring, and spacious, eat-in kitchen. Large family room with stone front fireplace. Plenty of room to spread out with both a living room and a family room plus a great deck and large yard for entertaining. Close to all major shopping centers and amenities. Don't miss this one.
